      • howMuchTimeTo

        int howMuchTimeTo​(int pos)
        Tell how much time the vehicle needs to arrive to position in current ride. It also gives negative values for stops that has already been visited this ride.
        Parameters:
        pos - is the list index to line route coordinate list
        Returns:
        amount in app seconds that the vehicle need to get to position (can be negative)

      • howMuchTimeToNext

        int howMuchTimeToNext​(int pos)
        Tell how much time the vehicle needs to arrive to position. It returns only positive values how many time it will take for the vehicle to get to stop.
        Parameters:
        pos - is the list index to line route coordinate list
        Returns:
        amount in app seconds that the vehicle need to get to position
